data.description: ** VA ASSUMABLE RATE of 2.875%** This meticulously maintained 3-bedroom, 2-bath home boasts a living area of 1,080 square feet, set on an expansive lot measuring 10,513 square feet in the heart of the Florida Keys. Immerse yourself in the serene ambiance of this tropical haven, surrounded by a lush natural hardwood hammock and swaying palm trees. The property is a veritable Eden, featuring a variety of fruit trees including Key limes, mangoes, bananas, hot peppers, and oranges, ensuring your own bountiful harvest year-round.Some key features of the home: Impact windows & doors, hardwired smoke detectors, metal roof, on demand hot water heater, emergency lighting, updated modern flooring and a shiplap living room wall that adds a touch of coastal charm.Imagine waking up to the sweet scent of citrus in your backyard, picking fresh fruits for breakfast, and enjoying them on your private patio. This property is not just a home; it's a lifestyle. Whether you're seeking a tranquil retreat, a tropical getaway, or a permanent residence in the Florida Keys, 21 Stirrup Key Blvd offers it all.  All insurances total $5739.00Don't miss the opportunity to make this captivating Marathon property your own. Contact us today to schedule a viewing and experience the allure of this tropical oasis for yourself. Paradise awaits!
